Klopp on the pitch: &quot;I could lie and say no (I'm not worried). The forecast is a bit better for tomorrow. We hope it will be okay.&quot;<br />
<br />
Klopp: &quot;We are out in Hong Kong checking different surfaces for us to train. In football you always have to find solutions.&quot;

Klopp: &quot;For me this (Asia Cup) is just pre-season, if I said that the best idea we&rsquo;ve had is to play a tournament in Asia, I&rsquo;d be lying!&quot;<br />
<br />
Klopp: &quot;We are all not happy about looking outside and seeing the rain and thinking &lsquo;can we train?'&quot;
